casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Moore, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Moore (1996), 77 Ohio St.3d 1203.]

(No. 95-1993 Submitted October 9, 1996 Decided November 6, 1996.) Ronald J. O’Brien, City Attorney, David M. Buchman, City Prosecutor, and Brenda J. Keltner, Assistant City Prosecutor, for appellee. Daniel D. Connor Co., L.P.A., and Daniel D. Connor, for appellant.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur.
